  title="Best eSIM Providers for Travel | Migrating Mammals"
  description="A curated comparison of the best eSIM providers for international travel. Compare Airalo, Holafly, Nomad, and Ubigi based on coverage, data plans, and price."
  canonical="https://migratingmammals.com/list-esim" schema={schema}
>
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>Best eSIM Providers for Travel</h1>
  <style>
:root {
      --danger: #ef4444;
      --success: #22c55e;
      --warning: #f59e0b;

}

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      background: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      padding: 60px 0 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);
